Check if the outdoor unit is covered or is installed near obstacles. Remove the coverings and obstacles.
Check if the Defrost function is on (page

). During defrost, the fan stops and warm air does not come out.
Check if doors or windows are open. This may cause poor circulation or performance. Close all doors and windows.
